'''''Condemnation''''' is a novel by [[Richard Baker]] published by [[Wizards of the Coast]] in 2003. It is the third book in the [[War of the Spider Queen (novel series)|War of the Spider Queen]] series.

{{Quote|''The forces aligned against [[Menzoberranzan]] begin to take shape, and the threat to [[drow]] civilization is more terrifying than anyone has yet imagined. From the impenetrable shadows of the [[Underdark]] to the remote corners of the no less unforgiving World Above, the path toward the secrets of [[Lolth]]'s silence is as unpredictable as it is deadly.''

''Joined by two drow who might be the last survivors of [[Ched Nasad]], the explorers from Menzoberranzan have learned much, but for every answer they find, a thousand new questions arise. They must seek out a rival priest, in hopes that he can speed them on their way to the goddess herself, but can one dark elf ever trust another?''}}
